Picaxe

Picaxe is a bitmap collision engine, which can be used to make terran destruction artillery games similar to scorched earth, worms armageddon, hedgewars or gunbound.

Picaxe is currently under development and is being ported from as3 source code.

http://scottcampbell.com.au/flash/terrain_destruction_game_engine_4

Picaxe Primary target is flash9+, however using NME we will be able to also target neko, javascript and c++.